ston Library  Don Samdahl  Colonel Head Librarian Erika Brooke Administrative Assistant Ph   540  464 7228 Fax   540  464 7279 ACCESS SERVICES Located on the 5th floor The Access Services Department manages Circulation and Interlibrary Loan services  The Circulation staff assist patrons by checking materials in and out of the library  searching for holdings  maintaining the reserve collection  ensuring that library materials are shelved in proper order  and answering basic questions about the library  At the request of VMI cadets and faculty  Interlibrary Loan staff borrow research materials not owned by Preston Library from other libraries in Virginia and the United States  Susie Hastings  Colonel Head of Access Services Ph   540  464 7607 Tonya Moore Interlibrary Loan Manager Ph   540  464 7570 Gwen Sichol Circulation   ILL Assistant Ph   540  464 7757 Alicia Wheeler Circulation Ph   540  464 7129  ARCHIVES Located on the 4th Floor The Archives manages the Institute s historic official records  manuscripts  photographs  19th century alumni biographical and genealogical information  Rare books and other rare materials are located in the VMI Archives  Diane Jacob  Colonel Head  Archives   Records Management Ph   540  464 7566 Mary Laura Kludy Archives   Records Management Assistant Ph   540  464 7516 Fax   540  464 7089 MEDIA SERVICES Located on the 4th Floor The Media Services Department provides services dealing with audio visual materials  including  reserving AV materials for rental or purchase  loaning AV equipment for classroom use  videotaping  editing  photography  satellite broadcast to cabled classrooms on post  duplication of video and audio tapes for academic use  dry mounting and laminating  and reference guidance for AV software and equipment rentals and purchases  Service requests must be made with as much advance notice as possible  Michael Brickler  Major Head of Media Services Ph   540  464 7655 REFERENCE Located on the 5th Floor The Reference Department coordinates library instruction  works with library patrons conducting research  and is available to answer more detailed research and general interest questions  Members of this department work with instructors to coordinate the use of library resources and with students on research projects  Accacia Mullen  Major Reference Librarian Ph   540  464 7250 Janet Holly  Colonel Reference Librarian Ph   540  464 7296 Gwen Sichol Circulation   ILL Assistant Ph   540  464 7757 TECHNICAL SERVICES Located on the 4th Floor The Technical Services Department manages the acquisition and cataloging of library materials  Tom Panko  Major Head of Technical Services Ph   540  464 7574 Susan Lemert  Ms  Acquisitions Assistant Ph   540  464 7568 Rachel Maderik  Major Systems and Technology Librarian Ph   540  464 7572 Sherry Teague  Ms  Cataloging Assistant Ph   540  464 7565   ALL STAFF Michael Brickler  Major Head of Media Services Ph   540  464 7655 Erika Brooke Administrative Assistant Ph   540  464 7228 Fax   540  464 7279 Susie Hastings  Colonel Head of Access Services Ph   540  464 7607  Janet Holly  Colonel Reference Librarian Ph   540  464 7296 Janine Hutchings Administrative Assistant Ph   540  464 7228 Diane Jacob  Colonel Head  Archives   Records Management Ph   540  464 7566 Mary Laura Kludy Archives   Records Management Assistant Ph   540  464 7516 Fax   540  464 7089 Susan LeMert Acquisitions Assistant Ph   540  464 7568 Tonya Moore Interlibrary Loan Manager Ph   540  464 7129 Rachel Maderik  Major Systems and Technology Librarian Ph   540  464 7572 Accacia Mullen  Major Reference Librarian Ph   540  464 7250 Tom Panko  Major Head of Technical Services Ph   540  464 7574 Don Samdahl  Colonel Head Librarian Gwen Sichol Circulation   ILL Assistant Ph   540  464 7757 Sherry Teague Cataloging Assistant Ph   540  464 7565 Alicia Wheeler Circulation Assistant Ph   540  464 7129 VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health  