nuscripts  photographs  19th century alumni biographical and genealogical information  Rare books and other rare materials are located in the VMI Archives  Diane Jacob  Colonel Head  Archives   Records Management Ph   540  464 7566 Mary Laura Kludy Archives   Records Management Assistant Ph   540  464 7516 Fax   540  464 7089 MEDIA SERVICES Located on the 4th Floor The Media Services Department provides services dealing with audio visual materials  including  reserving AV materials for rental or purchase  loaning AV equipment for classroom use  videotaping  editing  photography  satellite broadcast to cabled classrooms on post  duplication of video and audio tapes for academic use  dry mounting and laminating  and reference guidance for AV software and equipment rentals and purchases  Service requests must be made with as much advance notice as possible  Michael Brickler  Major Head of Media Services Ph   540  464 7655 REFERENCE Located on the 5th Floor The Reference Department coordinates library instruction  works with library patrons conducting research  and is available to answer more detailed research and general interest questions  Members of this department work with instructors to coordinate the use of library resources and with students on research projects  Accacia Mullen  Major Reference Librarian Ph   540  464 7250 Janet Holly  Colonel Reference Librarian Ph   540  464 7296 Gwen Sichol Circulation   ILL Assistant Ph   540  464 7757 TECHNICAL SERVICES Located on the 4th Floor The Technical Services Department manages the acquisition and cataloging of library materials  Tom Panko  Major Head of Technical Services Ph   540  464 7574 Susan Lemert  Ms  Acquisitions Assistant Ph   540  464 7568 Rachel Maderik  Major Systems and Technology Librarian Ph   540  464 7572 Sherry Teague  Ms  Cataloging Assistant Ph   540  464 7565   ALL STAFF Michael Brickler  Major Head of Media Services Ph   540  464 7655 Erika Brooke Administrative Assistant Ph   540  464 7228 Fa